Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:08.78,SONG_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur5\3c&H00A40D&}因为无数的回忆 会陪伴我左右{\fad(500,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:15.66,SONG_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur5\3c&H00A40D&}不带有一丝的痛苦和寂寞{\fad(500,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:21.92,SONG_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur5\3c&H00A40D&}试着对自己这样地诉说{\fad(500,500)}
